  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom + mezzanine cabins</strong> are around 45m² with 14m² mezzanine and sleep two to six people. Each cabin has two twin bedrooms, a single bed on the mezzanine, and a double sofa-bed in the open-plan living room/kitchen area. </p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Equipped kitchen with an oven, microwave, toaster, fridge, dishwasher and coffee maker</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Fireplace (small supply of wood included)</li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Iron </li>
<li>One shower </li>
<li>Two WC's - One upstairs and one downstairs</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made up on arrival</li>
<li>Final clean included (bins to be emptied before check out)</li>
<li>Cots with linen are free of charge, must be requested at the time of booking</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
